{"tid":1276663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港戰犯分類!","createTime":"2019-07-02T04:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T10:59:28.000Z","uid":294,"like":162,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7428ebc6251e363a5551cd2d12fe8e265bc7e864","tid":1276663,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:16:18.000Z","msg":"已經第三個PO 叫大家集中火力 <br />\n情願逐一擊破都唔好分散哂個風向, 就算過左突發事件之後, 都要考慮返個<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">優先次序</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n甲級戰犯:<br />\n-柒婆 <br />\n-英文好差果個死肥仔<br />\n-比加超<br />\n-第一日開槍果個俞XX (近排已經無人提, 唔該大家記撚住佢)<br />\n<br />\n乙級戰犯:<br />\n-前線黑警 (佢地係仆街, 但人數眾多, 武力又高, 成本太大。麻煩先針對英文好差果個死肥仔)<br />\n-奶共黨<br />\n<br />\n三級戰犯:<br />\n-藍絲, 初入職黑警, 奶共明星, 奶共KOL<br />\n-D咩奶共餐廳商鋪<br />\n<br />\n其他:<br />\n-親戚姨媽姑姐Facebook ig 港女臭雞講乜撚去其他台講唔該<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家和理非又好, 網戰又好, 「面對面傾計」都好<br />\n唔該大家集中目標 </span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69422d5498ba88ecaf29cfdb776a77faa21a7654","tid":1276663,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:16:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"115d1a39dcb153ef325ee02b6e25f5b326cdff4e","tid":1276663,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"4f7c44dfc79c18b3b15a0442aee426b8102d40d7","tid":1276663,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:18:02.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"739a3c624cf5c2b25476361aaca50d6a3c17856b","tid":1276663,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:19:17.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"33509d8ff9571e7413df0d824e7d9fe848c3b756","tid":1276663,"uid":164374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:21:26.000Z","msg":"保皇狗呢? 呢班撚屌 UN UN 腳, 一路指指點點, 一路等緊去美國過收成期"},{"pid":"906f40d56e386d5bedb8fa79b100ffde8daba444","tid":1276663,"uid"